WEBVTT

00:03:59.219 --> 00:04:03.963
(Smeh)

00:04:03.963 --> 00:04:05.411
Ali ne samo o konzervativcima.

00:04:05.411 --> 00:04:09.486
Takođe sam se uhvatila kako imam zlobne
misli o pekmezavim, liberalima centra

00:04:09.510 --> 00:04:11.388
i pohlepnim bankarima Vol Strita

00:04:11.412 --> 00:04:12.870
i islamofobima

00:04:12.894 --> 00:04:14.368
i sporim vozačima

00:04:14.392 --> 00:04:16.677
jer ja zaista mrzim spore vozače.

00:04:16.701 --> 00:04:19.220
(Smeh)

00:04:19.244 --> 00:04:22.244
I dok sam se hvatala
u tim trenucima licemerja,

00:04:22.268 --> 00:04:25.967
ili sam ih tek primećivala
ili su postajali sve gori,

00:04:25.991 --> 00:04:27.744
naročito u proteklih nekolik godina.

00:04:28.149 --> 00:04:30.274
I osećala sam sve više mržnje -